flow_raw_backup — license information
=====================================

Application code (flow_raw_backup.c), including the bundled minimal JSON
parser and the SHA-256 implementation, is released by the author into the
public domain / MIT (use freely, no warranty).

This application links against the following open-source components that are
part of the AXIS ACAP Native SDK / device firmware:

